TITLE: Episode 123 - Last Call with Brad Binkley and Dent [Adult Language]
DESCRIPTION: I don't know about you, but I am so glad that this stinker of a year is almost over. We've had some great times and some less than great times. But, this week, we are joined by Dent and Brad to celebrate and talk about 2021. The good, the bad, the ugly, and the hopeful. Join us for a good time with good friends.
